:: get back to sleep

I lie back down in my bed. The sun is still too bright, but now that I'm feeling better it's not so bad. I roll over to face away from the window.

Mom calls my cell around 2:30 to check up on me and remind me to take my Advil, which I do. After that, I take a box of tissues into the living room with me and watch T.V. until [[my parents get home]].

